On a rainy day at BTS practice room.  Jimin and Jungkook were alone practicing. 
But suddenly an unexpected argument arise. Jimin is very upset. 

Jm: Do whatever you want! 

The older between the two shouted. 
Jimin had enough.  And then he walks out to the practice room and leave Jungkook alone. Although its raining hard outside Jimin walks out of the pouring rain deciding to go home. 

After 20 minutes of walking going to their dorm.
Suddenly his phone rings. 
He saw the caller is Jk. He's angry but he still answer it.

"Hyung,  I'm really sorry" said a crying voice.  

"Yah, don't call me" Jimin answered back but he's worried.

At that moment Jimin felt pity to the younger boy. And felt conscience.

Jm: Yah.  Where are you? I will come and get you. 

Jimin asking worriedly.

Jm: Jungkook-ah.
Jk: I'm sorry hyung.

That day the two boys realize that they can't afford to lose each other.


Many was wondering how Jk and Jm was inseperable.  They are always together but I think this is the proof.
